                        "content": "A client in the primary health care provider’s (PHCP’s) office for an annual well visit asks the nurse about the differences between influenza and the common cold (viral rhinitis). The nurse would make which response to the client?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nInfluenza and the common cold, otherwise known as viral rhinitis, have various differences and similarities that assist in the diagnosis of each condition. Influenza is commonly associated with a high fever, whereas fevers with the common cold are rare. Therefore, option 2 is incorrect. Severe muscle pains, or myalgia, are common with the flu and rare with the common cold. Therefore, option 3 is incorrect. There is an annual vaccination available for influenza, not the common cold. Therefore, option 4 is incorrect. Influenza symptom onset is rapid, whereas symptom onset for the common cold is more gradual or insidious. Therefore, option 1 is the correct statement.",
                        "id": "569a4e29be59472194442948195b56ea",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "fb13ba21a276408b85ad98f85371e8f3",
                                "content": "Sinusitis"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "5c854f5ac1bb469db9b346f17ab3f394",
                                "content": "Influenza"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
